Subject:    <a href="?t=95837887600027&r=1&w=2">Re: Domain server WKS (Well Known Services)</a>
From:       <a href="?a=95837693400020&r=1&w=2">"Christopher A. Kent" &lt;cak () Purdue ! EDU&gt;</a>
